These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different games are played: chess, snooker, bridge
House: victorian, art-deco, modern
3 different pets are kept: turtle, pony, ferret
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, martial-arts, mystery
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, fonseca, tiparillo
City: hannover, nizza, colone
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, august, july
 1. the person who's birthday is in january is the person traveling to nizza##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in july is the person watching mystery movies##1
 3. the person playing bridge is between the person traveling to colone and the person playing snooker##2
 4. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
 5. the person watching martial-arts movies is the modern house##1
 6. the owner of the ferret is the person traveling to hannover##1
 7. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the victorian house##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
10. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Game      | snooker    | bridge   | chess           |
| House          | art-deco       | modern    | victorian         |
| Pet         | pony    | ferret  | turtle        |
| Movie-Genre           | spy | martial-arts   | mystery      |
| Cigar   | fonseca        | tiparillo    | swisher       |
| City   | nizza     | hannover  | colone       |
| Birthday         | january     | august | july |

