The people have 3 different jobs:  librarian, project-manager, bartender
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, emerald, lilac
House: colonial, palace, farmhouse
3 different games are played: scrabble, bridge, billiard
There 3 different types of food: apricot, plum, avocado
 1. the person playing billiard is in the middle##1
 2. the person traveling to venice is in the middle##1
 3. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
 4. the tiparillo-smoker is the project-manager##1
 5. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
 6. the farmhouse house is on the left of the project-manager##1
 7. the person eating avocado is between the person traveling to boston and the person who likes lavender##2
 8. the librarian is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 9. the project-manager is the person eating apricot##1
10. the farmhouse house is on the left of the palace house##1
11. the person eating apricot is the person who likes lavender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| City      | boston | venice      | colone      |
| Cigar         | cain     | baccarat     | tiparillo  |
| Job   | bartender | librarian  | project-manager |
| Color   | emerald  | lilac     | lavender |
| House           | colonial        | farmhouse | palace     |
| Game         | scrabble    | billiard | bridge   |
| Food     | plum        | avocado        | apricot   |

