3 different pets are kept: dog, craftsmansy, rabbit
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, fonseca, tiparillo
3 different games are played: domino, backgammon, whist
1. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
2. the person playing whist is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
