5. the person who growszinnia is between the person traveling to berlin and the german##2
6. the indian is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
7. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
8. the person playing domino is on the left of the modern house##1
9. the owner of the craftsmansy is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1

