6. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing domino##1
7. the person who's birthday is in january is the person watching disaster movies##1
8. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
9. the person traveling to venice is between the person watching disaster movies and the person playing canasta##2

